name.jp: エンジェル売り子ショップ

description.en: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.ar: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.br: Um fofo Anjo que gerência uma Loja Pessoal para você! Clique duas vezes para fechar a Loja. Você recebe o item de volta quando a loja é fechada.
description.cns: 天使替身娃娃，双击关闭商店。
description.de: Ein süßer Engel verwaltet deinen privaten Shop für dich! Doppelklicke um den Shop zu schließen.
description.fi: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fil: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fr: Un Ange mignon qui gère une boutique pour vous ! Double-cliquez pour fermer la boutique. Vos objets vous seront rendus.
description.id: Malaikat lucu yang mengelola Personal Shop untuk Anda! Klik dua kali untuk menutup Shop. Anda mendapatkan barang kembali saat Shop tutup.
description.it: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.jp: 個人商店の経営を代行してくれるかわいい天使！バフアイコンをダブルクリックするとショップを閉じることができます。ショップを閉じるとアイテムがインベントリに戻ります。
description.kr: 당신을 위해 개인 상점을 관리하는 귀여운 천사! 상점을 닫으려면 두 번 클릭하세요. 상점이 닫히면 아이템을 돌려받습니다.
description.nl: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.pl: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.ru: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.sp: ¡Un lindo Ángel atendiendo una Tienda Personal por tí! Doble click para cerrar la Tienda. Recuperarás el objeto cuando se cierre la Tienda.
description.sw: A cute Angel managing a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.th: นางฟ้าน่ารักจัดการร้านค้าส่วนตัวให้คุณ! ดับเบิ้ลคลิกเพื่อปิดร้าน ได้ของคืนเมื่อร้านปิด
description.tw: 可愛的天使為你管理個人商店，雙擊可以關閉商店，當商店關閉時物品將會返回
description.vi: Một Thiên thần dễ thương quản lý một Cửa hàng cá nhân cho bạn! Nhấp đúp để đóng Cửa hàng. Bạn nhận lại hàng khi Shop đóng cửa.
